Known for his many histrionics, Ayodele Fayose, governor of Ekiti, Tuesday circulated a photo of himself sewing on a machine. There had been other pictures in the past of the governor in funny get ups, eating yam flour, riding motorcycle and helping to put out a fire.
Fayose seems to have mastered the tricks showing an unusualness aimed at getting masses appeal.
